MOTION DOCKET

90-2274. In re Jane Doe

1. Hamilton County, No. C-900825. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to seal, IT IS ORDERED by the court that the record in this case, including all filings made by appellant with this court, be sealed, effective December 11, 1990.
